NUMBER 391
NAME Palace, Treasure Room
DEEPCAVE
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Smoky light, from sputtering torches, gleams off the mounds of treasure contained in this chamber. Chests and coffers burst at the seams with coins, gems, and items of magic. Swords, shields, armor and other weapons hang on the walls. Silks, spices, and objects d'art complete the impressive items of wealth that are gathered here in the Royal Treasure Chamber. An archway leads back to the palace.
*DESCRIPTION_END
